high_descs: Turn around and head to the cabinet across the room.
Open the top cabinet and retrieve the dishsponge from inside it.
Turn right and walk to the plate in the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the dishsponge on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it.
Enter the room on your right and walk to the right side of the shelf.
Put the plate on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put DishSponge on Plate on Shelf.

high_descs: Go straight reach on the top cabinet.
Pick the dishsponge from the top on the shelf.
Turn right and go straight to reach the plate on your left.
Put the dishsponge into the fridge.
Put the soap into the plate kept on the fridge.
Collect the plate from the shelf along with the soap.
Turn right to reach the table and put the plate along with the soap on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the DishSponge along with the Plate on the Shelf.

high_descs: Head to the cabinet above the sink.
Pick up the dishsponge from the cabinet.
Turn right to face the plate.
Put the dishsponge on the plate in the fridge.
Pick up the plate from the fridge.
Turn right to enter the room and turn left to reach the rightmost top shelf.
Put the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the DishSponge on the Plate and place it on the Shelf.
